OL,3,CCouncil considers changing black bin
OL,4,Ccollections to once a month
OL,6,FBlack bin collections in Bristol could
OL,7,Fbe reduced to once a month as the city
OL,8,Fcouncil considers "draft options".
OL,10,FThe plans include potentially reducing
OL,11,Frecycling days to "less frequently
OL,12,Fthan weekly" if one wheelie bin for
OL,13,Fall reusable materials is introduced.
OL,15,FAnother proposal includes one wheelie
OL,16,Fbin each for paper and card, plastic
OL,17,Fand cans, and glass, with each
OL,18,Fcollected three-weekly on rotation per
OL,19,Fweek.
