OL,3,CCouncil considers changing black bin
OL,4,Ccollections to once a month
OL,6,FIt follows a similar decision by South
OL,7,FGloucestershire Council to cut
OL,8,Fcollections of non-recyclable
OL,9,Fhousehold waste from every two to
OL,10,Fthree weeks.
OL,12,FThe leaked council document said:
OL,13,F"Through changes in regulation and
OL,14,Fincreasing operational, inflation and
OL,15,Finvestment costs, our waste and
OL,16,Frecycling service is facing an
OL,17,Fadditional bill of #5 million to #9
OL,18,Fmillion per year.
