OL,6,F"Without cost reductions we may need
OL,7,Fto reduce services and performance
OL,8,Fstandards. This amount will be reduced
OL,9,Fif we can recycle more and waste less."
OL,11,FIt said the council had considered
OL,12,Fthree options.
OL,14,FKeeping the service as it was would
OL,15,Fmean no reduction in carbon emissions
OL,16,Ffrom recycling and potential increased
OL,17,Fexposure to future carbon taxes.
