OL,6,FIt would also mean between #500,000
OL,7,Fand #1 million would have to be spent
OL,8,Fon public educational campaigns to
OL,9,Fmaintain current levels of performance.
OL,11,FAnother proposal, reducing black bin
OL,12,Fcollections to three-weekly, would
OL,13,Fboost the recycling rate by about six
OL,14,Fper cent, with about 40 per cent
OL,15,Freduction in carbon emissions from
OL,16,Fcollecting and treating waste and
OL,17,Frecycling.
OL,19,FThis would result in a saving of about
OL,20,F#1 million.
