OL,3,CCouncil considers changing black bin
OL,4,Ccollections to once a month
OL,6,FA third option, collecting black bins
OL,7,Fonce every four weeks, would increase
OL,8,Fthe recycling rate by 10 per cent and
OL,9,Fthere would be a 50 per cent drop in
OL,10,Fcarbon emissions, while an estimated
OL,11,F#2million would be saved.
OL,13,FThe proposals apply to households
OL,14,Fonly, not businesses or flats with
OL,15,Fcommunal collections or mini-recycling
OL,16,Fcentres where more support and service
OL,17,Fimprovements would be provided to
OL,18,Fincrease recycling, the document said.
