OL,3,CCouncil considers changing black bin
OL,4,Ccollections to once a month
OL,6,F"This change needs to be in our city's
OL,7,Fbehaviours and attitude towards waste
OL,8,Fand recycling as well as changes in
OL,9,Fhow we manage our city's waste systems
OL,10,Fand the financing of such services."
OL,12,FCllr Fodor added: "All options remain
OL,13,Fdraft proposals at this stage and no
OL,14,Fdecisions have been taken and no
OL,15,Fdecision will be taken on significant
OL,16,Fchanges to the future of waste and
OL,17,Frecycling services in our city without
OL,18,Fconsulting with residents and engaging
OL,19,Fwith businesses first."
